                <h1>University names main quad after West Campus architect Abele </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/5f6bc6f1-a448-437f-8646-e8dfb8da70e0.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;The&#x20;University&#x20;announced&#x20;Tuesday&#x20;that&#x20;the&#x20;main&#x20;quad&#x20;will&#x20;be&#x20;named&#x20;after&#x20;Julian&#x20;Abele,&amp;nbsp&#x3B;the&#x20;architect&#x20;of&#x20;West&#x20;Campus.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>The University announced Tuesday that the main quad will be named after Julian Abele,&nbsp;the architect of West Campus.&nbsp;</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/carolyn-chang">Carolyn Chang</a> |
                                                                                                                                The Chronicle
